The '''Conférence des Présidents d'Université''' (CPU) is an organization of university presidents in [[France]].<ref name="legifrance">[http://www.legifrance.com/affichCode.do;jsessionid=BEC86622FDC98CA92E02BB124EE86821.tpdjo09v_2?idSectionTA=LEGISCTA000006166797&cidTexte=LEGITEXT000006071191&dateTexte=20101001 LegiFrance]</ref>

==Overview==
The ''Conférence des Présidents d'Université'' was created in 1971.<ref>[http://www.cpu.fr/Presentation.238.0.html?&L=vdrdoetouwjmncn Présentation] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716103047/http://www.cpu.fr/Presentation.238.0.html?&L=vdrdoetouwjmncn |date=2011-07-16 }}</ref><ref>[https://archive.is/20120803095215/http://www.latribune.fr/entreprises/web-tv-transformation/les-sagas-de-la-transformation/20091218trib000454514/conference-des-presidents-d-universite-.html La Tribune]</ref> Its meetings are not open to the public.<ref name="legifrance"/> Its current president is [[Louis Vogel]], former President of [[Panthéon-Assas University]].

