iu, former Cultural Secretary of Embassy of China in DPR Korea and Republic of Korea,<ref name="York2014"/> master's degree of Korean Literature and Arts, secretary general of Communist Party of Chinese Students in Kim Il-Sung University, recipient of the Kim Il-sung Medal. * [[Ri Sol-ju]],<ref name="York2014"/> wife of North Korean leader Kim Jong-un.
